{"type":"message","id":"9b87d28b","parentId":"7c3a1a79","timestamp":"2026-03-25T06:14:02.697Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"很好，所有文件都已暂存。现在提交代码。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1134fa21e6d34d3685298b37","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw/tang-sansheng/projects/tianyou-platform && git commit -m \"feat(docker): 完成P3-01 Docker容器化配置\n\n【兵部】Phase 3平台优化 - 任务1完成\n\n变更内容：\n1. 优化后端API Dockerfile\n   - 多阶段构建优化层缓存\n   - 添加非root用户运行\n   - 集成健康检查\n   - 优化镜像大小\n\n2. 创建前端Blazor Dockerfile\n   - 多阶段构建\n   - 使用Nginx提供静态文件\n   - 配置Blazor路由支持\n   - Gzip压缩和缓存优化\n\n3. 完善docker-compose.yml\n   - 添加所有服务的健康检查\n   - 配置资源限制（CPU/内存）\n   - 环境变量统一管理\n   - 日志轮转配置\n   - 服务依赖关系优化\n\n4. 创建配置文件\n   - .env.example 环境变量示例\n   - nginx.conf 前端服务器配置\n   - .dockerignore 优化构建上下文\n\n5. 文档和工具\n   - DOCKER_DEPLOYMENT.md 部署指南\n   - validate-docker-config.sh 验证脚本\n\n技术栈：\n- ASP.NET Core 8.0\n- Blazor WebAssembly\n- PostgreSQL 15\n- Redis 7\n- RabbitMQ 3.12\n- Nginx 1.25\n\n任务状态：✅ 已完成\n下一步：P3-02 API性能优化\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":207,"output":355,"cacheRead":23936,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24498,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774419220787}}
